  "subject": "Fix: Modernize docs config and fix RTD build",
  "commit_message": "Fix: Modernize docs config and fix RTD build\n\nRemove sphinx_toolbox.collapse from conf.py and sphinx-toolbox from\nrequirements-docs.txt. The extension is unused in this repository and\nsphinx-toolbox 4.1.2 is incompatible with Sphinx 9.x, breaking RTD builds.\n\nSwitch tox.ini from remote upper-constraints URL to a local\netc/upper-constraints.onap.txt file, avoiding build failures when\ngit.onap.org returns HTTP 500 errors. Update basepython from 3.12\nto 3.13 to match .readthedocs.yaml and the doc repo.\n\nUpdate .readthedocs.yaml to ubuntu-24.04 and Python 3.13 (RTD\nubuntu-20.04 deprecated, removed June 2026).\n\nSee the doc repo for full sphinx-toolbox migration guidance.\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nChange-Id: Ibb2fa08a771eef9cd90c2af1e1b1443e0669ea21\nSigned-off-by: Matthew Watkins <mwatkins@linuxfoundation.org>\n",
